Description

AdditionalAuthentication is a custom annotation to mark methods that require an additional JWT authentication.

This class represents a custom exception for JWT (JSON Web Token) authentication.
JWTUtils
JWTUtils is a utility class responsible for generating, verifying, and managing JSON Web Tokens (JWTs).
LoggingAspect
LoggingAspect class provides a central place of code that logs entering and leaving methods.

UserFlightIdDto.UserFlightIdDtoBuilder
